			  	Good point. Well, if you are not going to be online all the time or you don't have script for ship pool investment, then building MB is still a good choice since it affects the % of PP you spend on building ships. However, generally you will be better off building F and have high production bonus. An obvious example would be the neutral power declaration project. It seems to reduce military but the production and commerce bonus will actually give you faster building rate in the long run. (might be debatable though)<p><br>___________________<br />
