			  	yea, production increases ship building, and another note, and ive herd this alot, people say that cheeper ships take the same amount of time to build as normal ships (refering to targoid 20% cheeper ships with bio armour), and thats not true, PP goes into the ship building pool, once it reaches the amount for the ship its building, it finishes, now if the ship costs less, it reaches that target at a lesser amount, thous, making it build faster<br />
